{"type":"message","id":"02420510","parentId":"96eabe89","timestamp":"2026-05-13T21:00:32.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, there are new changes. Now I need to spawn a sub-agent to run the Unity hot update pipeline. Let me create the sub-agent task. According to TOOLS.md:\n\n- The sub-agent should execute the bat file directly via exec: `\"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\"`\n- After completion, it should notify the group with @兵王(周以天)\n\nLet me also send a message to the group saying the update process has started.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"最新提交: `3cb5c058ce1` — 有代码变更，开始启动 sub-agent 执行热更流水线。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_6jAVvFIS6VkdudGswVQG3058","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77","message":"检测到代码更新，开始执行热更流水线（打资源+上传CDN）..."}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_vPFCwhzCR9XdvwStKpqv9009","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"执行热更流水线（打资源+上传CDN）\n\n## 任务\n1. 运行 Unity 热更流水线 bat 文件（路径: E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat）\n   - 直接通过 exec 运行此 bat 文件，不要包裹 cmd /c 或 powershell -Command\n   - 命令: \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\RunBuildPipelineHotUpdate.bat\"\n2. 等待流水线执行完成\n3. 流水线完成后，通过飞书消息在群 oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77 中发送通知：\n   - 内容：@兵王(周以天) 测试服更新完成\n   - action: send, channel: oc_59afc01122ec0cd04ca4d8c5103c7a77\n   - 同时单独通知主人（ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f）测试服已更新\n\n重要：如果正在执行或有 Unity 进程正在运行热更流水线（RunHotUpdatePipeline），则直接退出。\n完整日志输出会生成到 BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log（在 bat 同目录）。","mode":"run"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":176,"output":590,"cacheRead":14848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15614,"cost":{"input":0.00002464,"output":0.0001652,"cacheRead":0.000415744,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000605584}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778706027949,"response